  <description>
    <p>Azahar is an open-source 3DS emulator based on Citra, created as a merge between PabloMK7's Citra fork and Lime3DS.</p>
    <p>Our mission is to create the definitive platform for future development of Citra, a discontinued 3DS emulator.</p>
